group_1.textCenter: Well, I'm glad you came all the way to see@little old me...
'Fraid I'll have to disappoint you, though.
I can't go around talkin' about myself that@easily.
Still, I hope you can understand where I'm@comin' from.
I'm already a mysteeerious Coordinator, y'know?
Talkin' about myself takes one heck of a toll@on me.
It's not like *everything's* gotta be a secret,@either.
Feel free to ask about whatever y' feel like,@as long as it's not about myself.
